22
00:04:30,270 --> 00:04:32,352
<i>The country was shrinking,</i>

23
00:04:32,452 --> 00:04:35,034
<i>and there was life to be made out West...</i>

24
00:04:35,108 --> 00:04:38,703
<i>for any man with drive
and ambition.</i>

25
00:04:38,778 --> 00:04:42,908
<i>If your dream was big enough
and you had the guts to follow it,</i>

26
00:04:42,982 --> 00:04:46,816
<i>there was truly a fortune
to be made.</i>

27
00:04:55,627 --> 00:04:58,192
How are you, sir?

28
