124
00:14:39,478 --> 00:14:43,107
<i>Displaced families
took to the American highway...</i>

125
00:14:43,182 --> 00:14:46,549
<i>in the last possession
that remained to them:</i>

126
00:14:46,619 --> 00:14:49,588
<i>Their automobile.</i>

127
00:14:51,423 --> 00:14:55,052
<i>And all at once,
millions of Americans...</i>

128
