Everything.

143
00:17:07,693 --> 00:17:10,321
Dickens, Wordsworth.

144
00:17:10,396 --> 00:17:14,045
<i>There's your Arabian Nights
and Moby Dick,</i>

145
00:17:14,145 --> 00:17:15,595
<i>even your Milne, from when you were...</i>

