600
01:05:53,082 --> 01:05:56,779
- That's fine.
- I don't know when I can pay you back.

601
01:05:57,954 --> 01:06:00,889
I mean, when we win.
When we win, I can pay you back.

602
01:06:00,957 --> 01:06:04,415
