the biggest horse out there.

635
01:08:42,151 --> 01:08:45,348
<i>So you got big plans
for this little horse?</i>

636
01:08:45,421 --> 01:08:47,685
<i>Oh, yeah. See, sometimes
when the little guy,</i>

